data.title: MDWFP Hunting and Fishing Licenses
data.text:
Enter your Driver's License Number, State in which Driver's License was issued, Date of Birth, and State of Residence. After entering the information, please click CONTINUE.

In order to purchase a Hunting and Fishing License online, you must have a:

Valid Driver's License (if under the age of 16 use Social Security Number). Please do not include dashes or spaces while entering your Driver's License Number.

Hunter's Education Number (if born on or after January 1, 1972). This is not required for Fishing licenses or Electronic Waterfowl Stamps.

All major credit and debit cards accepted.
